@Lysimach | Make Polis Great just my thoughts on your question regarding scream factions and inter-faction competition. 

The factions are big team buckets, but we might be able to say that there is competition within the faction as to who gets the LP, at an individual level (and guild level despite guilds not being a thing in scream v0). 

Whether it's seen as competition with faction members or working with faction members to achieve goals is up to the guilds in a faction I would say personally
